$interpreted: Leah: AHHH!
Tica: Who's calling!? Wait, I'm coming!
Tica: Never fear! Whistlewood Valley's peace will be kept while I'm here!
Tica: You're alright now.
Leah: WOW~ Such powerful arcane magic, are you a student at the Rune Academy?
Tica: Mhm, that's right! I'm the Headmaster's pupil!
Leah: Well hi there sister, I'm Leah~ I want to study at the Rune Academy so badly!
Leah: But I can't find the entrance. I keep getting lost...
Tica: That's because ordinary folks can't just stroll right in. Finding the entrance is a newcomer's first exam!
Leah: I'm not eligible for the Rune Academy? Is it because I'm a demihuman?
Tica: No no no! There's all kinds of students Rune Academy!
Leah: Would you be willing to take me to the entrance?
Tica: That's against the rules. Plus, I'm on a mission...
Leah: Oh~ What kind of mission is it?
Tica: I can't tell you~It's a secret mission from the Headmaster himself...
Leah: Whoa, sister! You're really something! Must be very talented for the Headmaster to send you on a secret mission~
Leah: Is it dangerous?
Tica: Well... Alright, I'll let you in on the secret, but don't tell anyone else!
Tica: Headmaster wants me to find another one of these seed, but I don't even know where to begin...
Leah: A scavenger hunt? Us demihumans have the best sense of smell. Perhaps I can be of help~
Tica: REALLY?
Leah: Yup~ I think I know where it is.
Tica: Where where where? Tell me now, pretty please!
Leah: Let's make a deal, after I find the  seed, you'll take me to entrance of the Rune Academy!
Tica: Um... I don't know......
Leah: Just don't let the Headmaster find out?
Tica: How come I didn't think of that! Off we go~
Leah: Teehee, so lucky! What a dummy~
